fields.description:
Google has released a new Map SDK specific to Enterprises that provides extended functionality and monitoring to the GoogleMaps. As this is a new SDK, its currently not supported by our standard Maps Module. 

Information on GoogleMaps for Work can be found here:
https://www.google.com/work/mapsearth/
fields.summary: Support GoogleMaps for Work in Titanium
